claim.claim-text:
5. A wireless communication system comprising:
the terminal apparatus according to claim 4;
and a base station apparatus comprising a radio transmitting/receiving apparatus comprising:
a reception unit which receives, from a WI urinal apparatus, a measurement report indicative of a result of reception quality measurements taken at a femto cell contained in a macro cell;
a handover request creating unit which creates a handover request for a femto cell of handover destination based on a physical cell ID and a unique cell ID of the femto cell of handover destination added to the measurement report, and
a transmission unit which transmits, to the terminal apparatus, an instruction for handover to the femto cell based on a response to the handover request from the femto cell of handover destination.
